 nowrap><b><font color='white' face='Verdana' size='2'>Neimhidh</font></b></td>
        <TD bgcolor='black' valign='top'><font color='white' face='Verdana' size='2'> I have been camping the single tree spec the only times I have to run is when there is lag.  Here is what I do:</P><P>Prep time-<BR>Animate Dead<BR>/Pet taunt off<BR>Intensify Death as needed.</P><P>Pull time-<BR>Dooming Darkness<BR>/pet attack<BR>Dooming Darkness if resisted before, recast until it sticks.<BR>Boil Blood<BR>Eternities Torment<BR>Shock of Poison<BR>Shock of Poison<BR>Spirit Tap as needed.</P><P>Don't waste mana on fear, since dots do full damage I just kite him around until he dies.  Then I med and wait for respawn.  This might be harder if you do not have sow/jboots.  I have been doing this since level 31 and I know it works.</P><P></P><P>Neimhidh Draiocht<BR>Level 31 Necromancer of Cazic Thule<BR>Enchanting Souls<BR>Karana Server</font></td>
